  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses 12% growth and a 9% discount rate. Given the current valuation multiple, the market appears to be pricing in aggressive growth or a lower discount rate. Explore how different assumptions alter the intrinsic value.</p>

  <div class="table-wrap">
